What you need to know:  The Eldoret leg will be the 12th event in the Gold Tour in the 2021/2022 Series where athletes accumulate points towards the series.A combined amount of more than $400,000 (Sh40 m) in prize money is on offer for the best tour performers, including a new pool of $75,000 (Sh 7.5m) for the best male and female cross country runners.